Package info.papyri.dispatch.browse.facet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanFacet
    Extends the Facet class to deal specifically with Boolean fields.
    DateFacet
    The Facet used for setting and displaying date constraints.
    Facet
    Handles all the necessary backend (Solr) and frontend (HTML) interactions needed for selection of constraint values within a single facet.
    FacetBrowser  
    HasImagesFacet
    Facet class for selecting records based on the availability of images within papyri.info, online more generally, or in print publications.
    HasTranscriptionFacet
    Facet regarding whether or not a transcription is associated with a record.
    IdentifierFacet
    Facet for selecting texts based on DDbDP/HGV series, APIS collection, volume, and id number.
    LanguageFacet
    Facet for selection by language
    NomeFacet
    Facet allowing selection by nome
    PlaceFacet
    Facet for selection by provenance.
    StringSearchFacet
    Facet complex string-search capability.
    TranslationFacet  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FacetParam
    Enum of the names used in relation to the various Facets in HTML form elements
    IdentifierFacet.IdParam
    Enum giving the different elements in the classification hierarchy.
    StringSearchFacet.ClauseRole
    Values indicating the function of a given SearchTerm within a search.
    StringSearchFacet.SearchType
    Frontend descriptions of the type of search being performed.
